plot: Todd meet's Yolanda's parents, who don't know she's asexual. Mr. Peanutbutter romances a young waitress. Gina confesses a childhood dream to BoJack.

Todd and Yolanda have difficulty hiding their asexuality when they stay at her parents' house, BoJack convinces Flip and Princess Carolyn to listen to Gina's singing after learning she's obsessed with a Broadway musical, and Pickles and Mr. Peanutbutter have a non-date in the desert to watch the explosion of the International Space Station.—patricio-53898
